e检测数据改变原理</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#15-%E6%A8%A1%E6%8B%9FVue%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%9B%91%E6%B5%8B"><span class="toc-text">15. 模拟Vue对象数据监测</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#16-Vue-set%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8"><span class="toc-text">16. Vue.set方法的使用</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#17-%E6%A8%A1%E6%8B%9FVue%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%9B%91%E6%B5%8B%E4%B8%8E%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86"><span class="toc-text">17. 模拟Vue数组数据监测与原理</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#1-%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88"><span class="toc-text">1. 第一种方案</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#2-%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E7%A7%8D%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88"><span class="toc-text">2. 第二种方案</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#18-%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93Vue%E7%9B%91%E6%B5%8B%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86-%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1-%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84"><span class="toc-text">18. 总结Vue监测数据原理&#x2F;对象&#x2F;数组</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#1-Vue%E7%9B%91%E6%B5%8B%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86-Vue%E4%BC%9A%E7%9B%91%E8%A7%86data%E4%B8%AD%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E5%B1%82%E6%AC%A1%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE"><span class="toc-text">1. Vue监测数据的原理: Vue会监视data中所有层次的数据</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#2-%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E7%9B%91%E6%B5%8B%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE"><span class="toc-text">2. 如何监测对象中的数据?</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#3-%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E7%9B%91%E6%B5%8B%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE"><span class="toc-text">3. 如何监测数组中的数据?</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-l